        ///   location.  This happens only when saving to a disk file.  This event
        ///   will not be invoked when saving to a stream.
        /// </description>
        /// </item>
        ///
        /// <item>
        /// <term>ZipProgressEventType.Saving_AfterRenameTempArchive</term>
        /// <description>
