        /// </item>
        ///
        /// <item>
        /// <term>ZipProgressEventType.Extracting_AfterExtractEntry</term>
        /// <description>
        ///   Set when an Extract() on an entry in the ZipFile has completed.
        ///   Properties that are meaningful: ArchiveName, EntriesTotal,
